{"word":"H3974 - מָאֹור - mâʼôwr - maw-ore' - Bright","slug":"H3974","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָאֹור</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâʼôwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-ore'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bright"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D0;&#x05E8;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D0;&#x05D5;&#x05E8;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D0;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D0;&#x05D5;&#x05E8; - ma&#x0302;'o&#x0302;r  ma&#x0302;'o&#x0302;r  m<sup>e</sup>'o&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h  m<sup>e</sup>'o&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h</b> - <i>(1,2) maw-ore', (3,4) meh-o-raw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H215\">H215</a>; properly a <i>luminous</i> body or <i>luminary</i>, that is, (abstractly) <i>light</i> (as an element); figuratively <i>brightness</i>, that is, <i>cheerfulness</i>; specifically a <i>chandelier: - </i>bright, light."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H215\">H215</a>, <a href=\"#/H216\">H216</a>, <a href=\"#/H217\">H217</a>, <a href=\"#/H218\">H218</a>, <a href=\"#/H219\">H219</a>, <a href=\"#/H221\">H221</a>, <a href=\"#/H222\">H222</a>, <a href=\"#/H223\">H223</a>, <a href=\"#/H224\">H224</a>, <a href=\"#/H2971\">H2971</a>, <a href=\"#/H2972\">H2972</a>, <a href=\"#/H3975\">H3975</a>"}]}